202
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:47,516
Oke. Sebentar lagi.

203
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:50,311
Kamu sangat rajin belajar, Taiga.

204
00:12:51,353 --> 00:12:53,939
Mari kita istirahat.

205
00:12:54,732 --> 00:12:57,026
Ya… Tunggu sebentar.

206
00:12:58,444 --> 00:13:00,779
Mari kita istirahat.

207
